00:16:33.542 --> 00:16:36.500
[singsongy]
Oh, Alice!

00:16:36.542 --> 00:16:38.667
Alice? [gasps]

00:16:38.708 --> 00:16:40.000
Azz?

00:16:40.042 --> 00:16:41.000
-[screams]
-Sheesh.

00:16:41.042 --> 00:16:42.000
It was so mean of you

00:16:42.042 --> 00:16:43.500
to leave me behind, Alice.

00:16:43.542 --> 00:16:45.542
I had to drop
all my work to rush here.

00:16:45.583 --> 00:16:48.292
The least you could have done
was escort me onto the grounds.

00:16:49.500 --> 00:16:51.000
Why are you here, Mother?

00:16:51.042 --> 00:16:52.375
Wasn't David watching you?

00:16:52.417 --> 00:16:54.083
[ASMODEUS' MOTHER]
Oh, I knocked him out

00:16:54.125 --> 00:16:56.500
with my Charmed Lap Pillow
Ear Cleaning.

00:16:56.542 --> 00:16:57.583
Down he goes.

00:16:57.625 --> 00:16:58.958
David?!

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.417
[ASMODEUS' MOTHER]
Oh, so you're Iruma, then.

00:17:01.458 --> 00:17:02.958
I'm Alice's mother

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:05.375
as well as the Thirteen Crowns'
Mistress of Seduction,

00:17:05.417 --> 00:17:07.625
Amuryllis Asmodeus.

00:17:07.667 --> 00:17:11.083
Just so you know, you're all
my Alice has been talking about.

00:17:11.125 --> 00:17:12.792
I heard that you created
something neat

00:17:12.833 --> 00:17:14.292
he called fireworks.

00:17:14.333 --> 00:17:16.917
So, what kind of
seduction magic is it?

00:17:16.958 --> 00:17:18.292
Stop that!

00:17:18.333 --> 00:17:20.000
Oh, hey. Professor Raim
was your student, right?

00:17:20.042 --> 00:17:21.792
Why don't we go say
hello to her? How about it?

00:17:21.833 --> 00:17:23.875
I'll be right back, Iruma sir.

00:17:23.917 --> 00:17:27.875
-[IRUMA] Okay.
-I'll see you soon, Iruma dear.

00:17:27.917 --> 00:17:29.500
-Mother!
-[chuckles]

00:17:29.542 --> 00:17:31.833
Don't use your wiles
on Master Iruma.

00:17:31.875 --> 00:17:35.625
[IRUMA] Everyone's got unique
family circumstances, I guess.

00:17:35.667 --> 00:17:39.167
But they are definitely more
themselves in front of family.

00:17:39.208 --> 00:17:41.125
[indistinct chatter]

00:17:41.167 --> 00:17:43.042
[inaudible dialogue]

00:17:44.083 --> 00:17:47.083
[chatter continues]

00:17:50.833 --> 00:17:51.875
Lucky them.

00:17:52.833 --> 00:17:53.958
[gasps]

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:56.208
What snack would
you like, grandson?

00:17:56.250 --> 00:17:57.250
Hey, Grandpa.

00:17:59.500 --> 00:18:02.292
Wait, I thought
you'd be working. So how...

00:18:02.333 --> 00:18:03.500
Not to worry.

00:18:03.542 --> 00:18:04.750
I promised I'd be back

00:18:04.792 --> 00:18:07.417
by Battler Presentation Day,
didn't I?

00:18:09.083 --> 00:18:13.333
Come now. Let's go and enjoy
the festival together.

00:18:13.375 --> 00:18:15.042
[gasps, chuckles]

00:18:16.500 --> 00:18:18.917
[BOY]
Yes, I am the lord of everything

00:18:18.958 --> 00:18:20.375
the light touches...

00:18:22.250 --> 00:18:25.125
the missing
Demon King, Derkila.

00:18:25.167 --> 00:18:26.750
Kneel before me!

00:18:26.792 --> 00:18:28.458
[ALL gasp]

00:18:28.500 --> 00:18:29.750
[IRUMA]
Whoa!

00:18:29.792 --> 00:18:31.625
Woo-hoo! Way to go.

00:18:31.667 --> 00:18:33.292
That was awesome, brother.

00:18:33.333 --> 00:18:35.917
Good job, Sabnock.
You were really cool.

00:18:35.958 --> 00:18:37.000
Is this your sister?

00:18:37.042 --> 00:18:39.042
Yeah. I'm his little sis,

00:18:39.083 --> 00:18:40.583
and my name is Sylvia.

00:18:40.625 --> 00:18:42.417
He doesn't get to
come home very much,

00:18:42.458 --> 00:18:44.583
so I'm happy to see him
whenever I do.

00:18:44.625 --> 00:18:47.167
-[IRUMA] That's nice.
-You here alone, little one?

00:18:47.208 --> 00:18:49.250
No, I came here
with my oldest brother.

00:18:49.292 --> 00:18:51.250
But I lost him
in like two seconds.

00:18:51.292 --> 00:18:52.250
You tell me now?!

00:18:52.292 --> 00:18:54.083
We must track him down!

00:18:54.125 --> 00:18:55.667
[IRUMA]
'Kay.

00:18:55.708 --> 00:18:57.167
Heya, Iruma.

00:18:57.208 --> 00:18:58.625
Destroy-the-target, huh?

00:18:58.667 --> 00:19:00.958
Those fireworks were incredible.

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:03.625
I'm ashamed I found
your abilities lacking before.

00:19:03.667 --> 00:19:05.125
Oh, don't be.

00:19:05.167 --> 00:19:07.042
Play some games,
if you're up to it.

00:19:07.083 --> 00:19:08.458
Wait, but I...

00:19:08.500 --> 00:19:10.500
These metal targets
are pretty tough, though.

00:19:10.542 --> 00:19:12.792
[ALL gasp]

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:17.208
[BOYS groan]

00:19:20.583 --> 00:19:21.458
[grunts]

00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:22.917
[IRUMA gasps]

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:30.000
[screams]

00:19:30.042 --> 00:19:31.708
[grunting rapidly]

00:19:31.750 --> 00:19:33.167
[GIRL]
We'll never financially recover.

00:19:33.208 --> 00:19:34.208
[IRUMA]
I'm so sorry.

00:19:34.250 --> 00:19:36.000
[WOMAN]
This is unacceptable.

00:19:36.042 --> 00:19:38.333
An adult stealing prizes
from my kid?

00:19:38.375 --> 00:19:40.458
-Who allows that?
-Uh-huh.

00:19:40.500 --> 00:19:43.083
You'd better do
something about this.

00:19:43.125 --> 00:19:45.083
I shall incarcerate them.

00:19:45.125 --> 00:19:46.083
[gasps]

00:19:46.125 --> 00:19:48.125
Please have mercy on me, sir!

00:19:48.167 --> 00:19:49.667
Would you look at this?

00:19:49.708 --> 00:19:51.125
[BOTH]
Huh?

00:19:51.167 --> 00:19:52.625
[WOMAN]
Professor Kalego?

00:19:52.667 --> 00:19:54.292
Well, what's gotten into him?

00:19:54.333 --> 00:19:55.625
[GIRL cries]

00:19:55.667 --> 00:19:58.667
♪

00:20:02.083 --> 00:20:03.542
[ALL]
Hmm.

00:20:15.667 --> 00:20:17.625
[ALL cheering]

00:20:17.667 --> 00:20:19.667
♪

00:20:39.708 --> 00:20:41.458
[DALI over PA]
Hello, everyone.

00:20:41.500 --> 00:20:44.667
The Party Day is sadly
drawing to a close soon.

00:20:44.708 --> 00:20:46.167
Have y'all had fun?

00:20:46.208 --> 00:20:48.208
[ALL]
Yeah!

00:20:50.208 --> 00:20:53.375
Funny. We really cleaned up
at the battler games.

00:20:53.417 --> 00:20:55.917
Opera shows
no weakness or mercy.

00:20:55.958 --> 00:20:59.458
You accepted gifts, too,
from students, if I recall.

00:20:59.500 --> 00:21:00.917
Well, I am a popular man.

00:21:00.958 --> 00:21:04.417
And it was my first time
participating, after all.

00:21:04.458 --> 00:21:07.083
I wanted to look good
for my darling grandson.

00:21:07.125 --> 00:21:09.083
Couldn't disappoint him.

00:21:09.125 --> 00:21:10.208
[IRUMA]
Aah.

00:21:11.750 --> 00:21:15.083
Well, well.
The whole Iruma family.

00:21:15.125 --> 00:21:16.625
Just get a load of this.

00:21:16.667 --> 00:21:19.208
My lazy sister couldn't make it
'cause she overslept.

00:21:19.250 --> 00:21:20.542
And my brother?

00:21:20.583 --> 00:21:22.625
He swiped my wallet
when I met him earlier.

00:21:22.667 --> 00:21:24.750
[LEAD]
Man, Iruma. You're so lucky.

00:21:24.792 --> 00:21:26.375
[JAZZ] Your family's
your pride and joy.

00:21:26.417 --> 00:21:27.875
[gasps]

00:21:27.917 --> 00:21:29.542
[sighs]

00:21:29.583 --> 00:21:30.917
[chuckles]

00:21:32.708 --> 00:21:34.500
You're right. Aren't they great?

00:21:36.667 --> 00:21:38.125
[SULLIVAN]
He said "Pride and joy."

00:21:38.167 --> 00:21:39.625
[giggles]

00:21:39.667 --> 00:21:42.000
Come on, let's take
a picture together.

00:21:43.417 --> 00:21:46.375
Okay, here we go. Now, smile.

00:21:46.417 --> 00:21:47.583
[camera shutter clicks]

00:21:47.625 --> 00:21:50.667
♪

00:21:53.542 --> 00:21:56.458
[DALI over PA] Now, an important
announcement from HQ.

00:21:56.500 --> 00:21:59.958
The results of the Battler Party
voting are tallied and final.

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:01.625
[ALL gasp]

00:22:01.667 --> 00:22:04.917
In just a moment,
I'm going to announce them.

00:22:04.958 --> 00:22:06.625
[groans uncomfortably]

00:22:06.667 --> 00:22:09.458
[IRUMA]
Kiriwo, about that grand prize,

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:11.542
well, we should go for it.

00:22:12.542 --> 00:22:16.042
[DALI] The Battler Party's
Indisputably

00:22:16.083 --> 00:22:21.500
Most Valuable Battler is...

00:22:21.542 --> 00:22:24.542
♪

00:23:55.542 --> 00:23:57.958
Su... ki... ma!

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.958
-[IRUMA moaning softly]
Look at him.

00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:01.750
Just sleeping like a baby.

00:24:08.500 --> 00:24:10.250
[giggling]

00:24:10.292 --> 00:24:12.042
[NARRATOR] Kiriwo messed
with the slumbering Iruma

00:24:12.083 --> 00:24:13.458
for quite a while.

00:24:15.250 --> 00:24:17.792
[KIRIWO] I didn't expect
Iruma to get in my way.

00:24:17.833 --> 00:24:21.333
But just remember,
malice is hidden all around us.

00:24:21.375 --> 00:24:24.667
And always be wary
of a demon's true nature.

00:24:25.667 --> 00:24:29.583
Next time "Glorious Award,"
and "Treatment of Humans."

00:24:30.667 --> 00:24:33.792
Man, those fireworks
sure were pretty.

00:24:33.833 --> 00:24:36.875
The MagiApp Battler winning
Most Valuable Battler

00:24:36.917 --> 00:24:38.875
might be within reach, Iruma.

00:24:38.917 --> 00:24:40.917
♪

